式，我们可以把
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:3.6.7"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

式写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\langle p^{\prime},s^{\prime}|J^{\mu}\left(0\right)|p,s\rangle=\bar{u}\left\{ \gamma^{\mu}[F_{1}(q^{2})+F_{2}(q^{2})]-\frac{1}{2m}(p^{\prime}+p)^{\mu}F_{2}(q^{2})\right\} u
\]

\end_inset

进而在处理
\begin_inset Formula $N^{\mu}$
\end_inset

时，我们把正比于
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{\mu}$
\end_inset

的项扔掉，只提取出
\begin_inset Formula $F_{2}(0)$
\end_inset

。把
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:3.6.9"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

中的
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

