\begin_inset Formula $l$
\end_inset

代换，得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
N^{\mu}=\gamma^{\nu}\left[\slashed{l}+\slashed{P}^{\prime}+m\right]\gamma^{\mu}\left[\slashed{l}+\slashed{P}+m\right]\gamma_{\nu}
\]

\end_inset

式中
\begin_inset Formula $P^{\prime\mu}\equiv(1-\alpha)p^{\prime\mu}-\beta p^{\mu}$
\end_inset

，而
\begin_inset Formula $P^{\mu}\equiv(1-\beta)p^{\mu}-\alpha p^{\prime\mu}$
\end_inset

。用
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

的幂次来整理
\begin_inset Formula $N^{\mu}$
\end_inset

的项比较方便：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $m^{2}$
\end_inset

项：一个
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma^{\mu}$
\end_inset

项，扔掉。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

项：按
\begin_inset Formula $l$
\end_inset

的幂次整理。由对称性，
\begin_inset Formula $l$
\end_inset

的线性项积分为
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

，因此，只剩下不含
\begin_inset Formula $l$
\end_inset

的项：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
m\left(\gamma^{\nu}\slashed{P}^{\prime}\gamma^{\mu}\gamma_{\nu}+\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\mu}\slashed{P}\gamma_{\nu}\right)=4m[(1-2\alpha)p^{\prime\mu}+(1-2\beta)p^{\mu}]\Rightarrow4m(1-\alpha-\beta)(p^{\prime}+p)^{\mu}
\]

\end_inset

最后一步使用了技巧：既然
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{D}$
\end_inset

在变换
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha\longleftrightarrow\beta$
\end_inset

下对称，那么我们可以对称化从
\begin_inset Formula $N^{\mu}$
\end_inset

中得到的项。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
最后是
\begin_inset Formula $m^{0}$
\end_inset

项，它是
\begin_inset Formula $l$
\end_inset

的二次项：由洛伦兹不变性，我们可以把
\begin_inset Formula $\int\dif^{4}l/(2\pi)^{2}$
\end_inset

内的
\begin_inset Formula $l^{\sigma}l^{\tau}$
\end_inset

等效替换为
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{4}\eta^{\sigma\tau}l^{2}$
\end_inset

（这一步的合理性是因为我们调整了积分变量，使
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{D}$
\end_inset

