\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

的幂次整理比较方便。用上前面用过的各种技巧，我们可以发现，
\begin_inset Formula $m^{2}$
\end_inset

项可以扔掉，
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

项给出
\begin_inset Formula $2m(p^{\prime}+p)^{\mu}[\alpha(1-\alpha)+\beta(1-\beta)]$
\end_inset

，而
\begin_inset Formula $m^{0}$
\end_inset

项给出
\begin_inset Formula $2m(p^{\prime}+p)^{\mu}[-2(1-\alpha)(1-\beta)]$
\end_inset

